{/* CHALLENGES SECTION                                                  */}
{/* ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ */}
{section === "challenges" && (
<div class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">

  <p class="mb-4">
    Blueberry Futures keeps things simple with two one-step challenges that share the same profit targets, drawdown sizes, contract limits, and 30-day window. The 50K, 100K, and 150K accounts all aim for $3,000, $6,000, and $10,000 targets, paired with $2,000, $3,000, and $4,500 max drawdowns. Your choice comes down to how you prefer the drawdown to behave: end-of-day safety on Ascent or real-time trailing risk on Accelerated.
